{"tid":2441092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國人最鐘意玩內鬥，而家鬥緊蘋果","createTime":"2021-03-10T12:08:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T12:32:57.000Z","uid":380132,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"76b9d2f4be71af880d3342a2122801bb76a4d9a4","tid":2441092,"uid":380132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:08:35.000Z","msg":"大家話岩唔岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7751494cb050ba983dd3f48aadb36a20f002b71a","tid":2441092,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:13:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/dlZo7sOiSKs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FdlZo7sOiSKs&d=86rwbh%2BN0C2BU4li7ttIPnr2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=5cd38b58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/dlZo7sOiSKs</a>"},{"pid":"c4bf6c69fd0fba7f0c07b0f496745d29d9d677e5","tid":2441092,"uid":88743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:18:25.000Z","msg":"今次蘋果議題buy time係重點<br />\n好多人就係要spin走buy time呢個point<br />\n將個焦點放係「封逃生門既係政府」度<br />\n<br />\n香港已經無左容許指出同路人錯誤，百屌成材既空間<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jrJNkyN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjrJNkyN.gif&h=af549e43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vz35RFs.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fvz35RFs.gif&h=a6566ee0&s={SIZE}\" />  <br />\n<br />\n​同類事件將會無數次重覆發生<br />\n之後香港人繼續將個責任推比政府<br />\n豬隊友永遠無責任<br />\n唔係要分化<br />\n百屌成材目的係要避免事件重覆發生<br />\n但有人將屌同路人等如分化<br />\n咁真係無野好講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette1.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/3/3b/YJm0-1-.gif/revision/latest?cb=20130725051312\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette1.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F3%2F3b%2FYJm0-1-.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20130725051312&h=f1f26999&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7b17ce678360eb0e6d34594f22bcd1788a6163f1","tid":2441092,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:31:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"736c1a865c9f9c72c2e50da278333c3d2f6a22c0","tid":2441092,"uid":95520,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T12:32:57.000Z","msg":"見到都覺得煩"}]}